    <p>
      Participants must be <strong>physically fit to complete a 4 km hike</strong> and are responsible for their own health and safety. Those with medical conditions should consult a healthcare professional before attending. <strong>Bringing a personal first aid kit is compulsory</strong>.
    </p>

    <h2>Age Requirements</h2>
    <p>
      Participants aged <strong>13 to 17 must attend with a responsible adult</strong>. All instructions from event organisers must be followed at all times.
    </p>

    <h2>Transport Arrangements</h2>
    <p>
      Transport arrangements are optional and available at a fee of <strong>R100 return</strong>. Transport fees must be paid by <strong>26 December 2025</strong>. <strong>No refunds will be issued once payment is made</strong>.
    </p>

